{"tha-ap302:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap302:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap302:0.3":"Anusamsavakattheraapadana ","tha-ap302:1.1":"“Pindaya caramanaham, ","tha-ap302:1.2":"vipassimaddasam jinam; ","tha-ap302:1.3":"Ulungabhikkham padasim, ","tha-ap302:1.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap302:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap302:2.2":"abhivadesaham tada; ","tha-ap302:2.3":"Anusamsavayim buddham, ","tha-ap302:2.4":"uttamatthassa pattiya. ","tha-ap302:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap302:3.2":"anusamsavayim aham; ","tha-ap302:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap302:3.4":"anusamsavana phalam. ","tha-ap302:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap302:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap302:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap302:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma anusamsavako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap302:6.1":"Anusamsavakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap302:6.2":"Citakapujakavaggo timsatimo. ","tha-ap302:7.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap302:8.1":"Citakam parichatto ca, ","tha-ap302:8.2":"saddagosisasantharam; ","tha-ap302:8.3":"Pado padesam saranam, ","tha-ap302:8.4":"ambo samsavakopi ca; ","tha-ap302:8.5":"Atthatalisa gathayo, ","tha-ap302:8.6":"ganitayo vibhavibhi. ","tha-ap302:9.1":"Atha vagguddanam ","tha-ap302:10.1":"Kanikaro hatthidado, ","tha-ap302:10.2":"alambanudakasanam; ","tha-ap302:10.3":"Tuvaram thomako ceva, ","tha-ap302:10.4":"ukkhepam sisupadhanam. ","tha-ap302:11.1":"Pannado citapuji ca, ","tha-ap302:11.2":"gathayo ceva sabbaso; ","tha-ap302:11.3":"Cattari ca sataniha, ","tha-ap302:11.4":"ekapannasameva ca. ","tha-ap302:12.1":"Pancavisasata sabba, ","tha-ap302:12.2":"dvasattati taduttari; ","tha-ap302:12.3":"Tisatam apadananam, ","tha-ap302:12.4":"ganita atthadassibhi. ","tha-ap302:13.1":"Kanikaravaggadasakam. ","tha-ap302:14.1":"Tatiyasatakam samattam. "}